snippet.title: C&C Red Alert: A Path Beyond - Games Convention '06 Trailer
snippet.description:
www.apathbeyond.com
Command & Conquer Red Alert: A Path Beyond 
trailer for the 2006 Leipzig Games Convention. 

 Not the best trailer ever, but it was made with limited time and footage.

Music: Hell March by Frank Klepacki [www.frankklepacki.com]
Video: Various people, thanks.
Editing: drunkill
